<h2 id="28-keyboard-shortcuts">2.8 Keyboard shortcuts</h2>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>Tab &amp; 1 2 3     toggle edit mode and select vertex, edge or face mode
ctrl + Tab      pie menu
shift + space   play (depends)
space           search (depends)
ctrl + space    fullscreen window
z               solid, wireframe ...
q               quick favorites
</code></pre></div></div>

